reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for concert
reviews.reviewText: Very cute and sturdy. This will work great for concerts. More than enough room for the essentials.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Classy & good size
reviews.reviewText: Love it! Perfect size to hold everything from a phone to keys and makeup. Looks great for all stadium events that have a clear bag policy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It fits the IPhone 14Pro
reviews.reviewText: Cute little transparent vinyl purse, and big enough to fit the IPhone 14Pro. I bought another one before finding this and returned because the phone wouldn’t fit. Nice chain that can be used as cross body as well as a shoulder bag.I would love to have the edges with a better finish, instead of the just “melting technique “ to sewing it shut. A gold metal edging or some nice fabric would be great and would disguise de somewhat raw edge. Cute otherwise.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 20, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars smaller than you'd think
reviews.reviewText: I got this purse to go to a concert in Raleigh. I wish I'd paid more attention to the measurements, because it's slightly smaller than what I'd expected. I wound up having to ditch my wallet and use a Ziploc with my ID/cards in it to make what I needed to fit work so that I could close the clasp on the purse. Overall though, this was a stylish option for a clear bag and seems to be well made.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect clear bag for concerts!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this for a "clear bag policy" concert and it did not disappoint. It looks much more expensive than it is, the gold hardware isn't too cheap-looking, and it was sturdy. I like that the flap has a mechanism to keep it closed. The cross-body style made me feel secure carrying it in a crowd. Definitely recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great stadium bag
reviews.reviewText: Got this last min for a comedy show. Downside it’s not adjustable but just tied a knot and used. Love it. I only carry essentials and it’s perfect.
